The term legend is used all too loosely in this day and age, with music arguably the worst offender.
 
But in Ray Charles, modern music has someone it can proudly label one of cultures true geniuses. 

Charles blazed his own trail through a career spanning nearly six decades and this 3CD, 75 track set celebrates his most popular, influential and seminal recordings.
